{"tid":746280,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【英國腔】睇網球決賽被外媒捕獲　陳奕迅曬流利英文仲高歌賀冠軍","createTime":"2018-07-17T12:21:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T15:46:10.000Z","uid":194525,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9800758f0815d44d049108f10d05f233ff136e7e","tid":746280,"uid":194525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T12:21:00.000Z","msg":"曾在英國留學的陳奕迅（Eason）說得一口流利英語，已為人所知，不少網民都喜歡「狂loop」他用英國口音受訪的片段。最近Eason受邀到倫敦看溫布頓網球錦標賽，竟被外國體育頻道捕獲訪問，分享對賽事的睇法及感受，更被邀請即場唱歌恭喜勝出的球員。網民看過其受訪影片都大讚Eason動聽的英式口音，聽起來是種享受。<br />\n<br />\n外國媒體FOX的亞洲體育頻道周日（15日）上載影片，當時西裝骨骨的Eason正享受英式下午茶，體育主持開場介紹他為「香港國際超級巨星、歌手及演員」，其後着Eason分享他對賽事看法，Eason亦用一口流利英語大談感受。<br />\n<br />\n他笑說自己是著名網球選手費達拿（Roger Federer）的球迷，但因來自南非的奇雲安達臣（Kevin Anderson）早前擊敗費達拿後，倒戈支持了他。不過奇雲安達臣最終在男單決賽，敗給塞爾維亞的祖高域（Novak Djokovic），但Eason仍大讚賽事精彩。對於現場觀賽的氣氛，Eason稱在溫布頓現場和在電視觀看賽事頗有分別，更指這是一個難忘的經歷。<br />\n<br />\n最後主持邀請Eason大開金口，高唱一曲祝賀祖高域奪得冠軍，更說英語或廣東話的歌曲也可以，令Eason相當尷尬，最後他唱了皇后樂團經典歌曲「We Are The Champions」其中一句，並改成「He is the champion of the world（他是世界冠軍）」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://youtu.be/sxOovQvEr0g\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsxOovQvEr0g&h=b14b63f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉自：香港01"},{"pid":"24298ca726922bdb9e4361f68da081054f2366a7","tid":746280,"uid":194525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T12:21:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sxOovQvEr0g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsxOovQvEr0g&d=DkTwdOgB6DuaSu5HvcQK%2FdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=6a033f59\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sxOovQvEr0g</a>"},{"pid":"4f1c17d1de5a9eea338a80419ee06e2b434ebca2","tid":746280,"uid":194525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T12:27:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/202734_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F202734_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=01199ee9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咁R鼻"},{"pid":"b810d8821ffd62aade9fa8ce6aa84de4e18f22ec","tid":746280,"uid":194525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T14:53:20.000Z","msg":"無人講下既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c7de3d16f8203c89cb64678164af40c71c0971","tid":746280,"uid":31173,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T15:06:40.000Z","msg":"得個accent姐，流唔流利就⋯"},{"pid":"a85dd82c3bda715ec014aa77210168bff2d520dd","tid":746280,"uid":188805,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T15:21:38.000Z","msg":"老老柒柒，好撚麻麻"},{"pid":"01a404c35ce7e0cfa10a49d35e14a980a38fa553","tid":746280,"uid":129340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"13c7de3d16f8203c89cb64678164af40c71c0971","tid":746280,"uid":31173,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T15:06:40.000Z","msg":"得個accent姐，流唔流利就⋯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T15:31:41.000Z","msg":"講得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d83136c7cac718b65e3d5b61067675bf404bdaba","tid":746280,"uid":44297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T15:34:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係外國聽過佢concert<br />\n全程流利英文"},{"pid":"711ff476897416d5ba71d0d6738176aa77913752","tid":746280,"uid":192409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T15:39:30.000Z","msg":"其實唔難"},{"pid":"09fcc12929bf1f46ebf79209c09d1e6d4e272342","tid":746280,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d83136c7cac718b65e3d5b61067675bf404bdaba","tid":746280,"uid":44297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T15:34:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係外國聽過佢concert<br />\n全程流利英文"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T15:42:58.000Z","msg":"啲觀眾全部中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor